Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-----OPlrcJPN-----
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.83,0:00:55.46,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}憧れを書きとめて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.59,0:00:58.21,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}いつか叶える日のために
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.30,0:01:03.68,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}折り目つけたあのページを　開きたい時がきた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.72,0:01:09.02,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}巻き起こるアレコレで　見失うこともあるけれど
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.10,0:01:11.77,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}ねっ、大丈夫　踏み出してる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.81,0:01:14.40,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}はじまりは想定外
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.56,0:01:17.19,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}君が消せないまま残した
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.27,0:01:19.94,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}寂しがりだった記憶さえ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.99,0:01:24.03,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}読み替えてみせるよ　明るい方へ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.07,0:01:29.45,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}たったそれだけで全てが変わる気がするから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.58,0:01:30.75,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}All Right
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.83,0:01:33.79,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}だから　さあおいで　そのままで！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.83,0:01:36.63,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}弱虫も隠さないで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.75,0:01:37.84,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}"On my Sheep"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.92,0:01:41.51,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}夢乗せ　待ち合わせよう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.67,0:01:47.39,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}この冒険記を綴る中　君の名を呼んでも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.47,0:01:53.89,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}もう迷子じゃない　一緒の旅を始めよう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.98,0:02:01.23,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}そう…きみと、わたし、もっと！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-----OPlrcCHN-----
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.83,0:00:55.46,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}记下你的憧憬
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.59,0:00:58.21,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}以迎接它变成现实的那天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.30,0:01:03.68,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}折叠起来的书页  正在呼唤着我去翻阅
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.72,0:01:09.02,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}扬起的风沙尘土  可能会让你迷失方向
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.10,0:01:11.77,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}但是不要担心  我们在坚定前行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.81,0:01:14.40,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}只是开端有点意想不到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.56,0:01:17.19,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}你记录下的寂寞经历
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.27,0:01:19.94,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}无法擦去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.99,0:01:24.03,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}但我会解读成未来的财富
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.07,0:01:29.45,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}如此小的努力就能让我感到世界焕然一新
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.58,0:01:30.75,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}All Right
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.83,0:01:33.79,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}所以  跟我来吧  就这样出发！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.83,0:01:36.63,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}没有什么好害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.75,0:01:37.84,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}"On my Sheep"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.92,0:01:41.51,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}放飞梦想  相约明天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.67,0:01:47.39,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}书写这篇历险记的时候  即使呼唤你的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.47,0:01:53.89,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}那也不意味着迷路  而是共同启程的信号
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.98,0:02:01.23,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}没错…你与我 不会停步！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-----EDlrcJPN-----
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.38,0:20:56.69,EDlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}始まりのベル　鍵をかける音
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.24,0:21:04.49,EDlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}流れゆく間に大人になる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.76,0:21:10.23,EDlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}走り　はしゃぎ　過ごす日々が
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.59,0:21:14.47,EDlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}遠ざかるときがくる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.79,0:21:18.97,EDlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}ここで出した答えを
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.97,0:21:31.16,EDlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}ああ　どこかで語り継げたら
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.97,0:21:36.44,EDlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}迷いながら歩く人波を
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.70,0:21:40.77,EDlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}照らし出す光になれるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.88,0:21:48.98,EDlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}包まれてたグリーンベルトの先
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.19,0:21:57.32,EDlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}続く明日を目指してる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-----EDlrcCHN-----
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.38,0:20:56.69,EDlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}起始之铃  上锁之声
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.24,0:21:04.49,EDlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}在它们的流淌中  我们逐渐成长
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.76,0:21:10.23,EDlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}奔跑欢笑的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.59,0:21:14.47,EDlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}终归会远去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.79,0:21:18.97,EDlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}此刻得出的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.97,0:21:31.16,EDlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}只要将它流传下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.97,0:21:36.44,EDlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}即使是迷惘而行的人潮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.70,0:21:40.77,EDlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}也能将其引领
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.88,0:21:48.98,EDlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}沿着绿荫大道走下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.19,0:21:57.32,EDlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}就能到达期望的明天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-----TXT-----
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.54,0:00:05.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很努力呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.38,0:00:07.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.27,0:00:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到家了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.79,0:00:35.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么情况
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.56,0:00:37.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从今天起就在一起住了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.65,0:00:39.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄妹能够亲密无间了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.61,0:00:40.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,京太郎哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.59,0:02:13.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.87,0:02:15.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我亲手做的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.00,0:02:17.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.84,0:02:21.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这饭做得这么用心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.76,0:02:23.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥我感激万分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.18,0:02:25.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟水是我烧的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.90,0:02:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笼统来说也能算是我亲手做的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.36,0:02:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太笼统了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.04,0:02:37.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.05,0:02:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么不好  兄妹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.30,0:02:42.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我开始觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.74,0:02:45.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,专程跑你这里看电视剧太麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.64,0:02:52.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.84,0:02:57.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么  就是在想我之前为什么没认出你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.06,0:03:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我只当了三个月你的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.69,0:03:04.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.20,0:03:07.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.60,0:03:13.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲失踪  家庭破碎之前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.75,0:03:21.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很短的一段时间里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.57,0:03:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小太刀曾经是我的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.02,0:03:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记不清她是父亲第几任妻子带来的孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.52,0:03:38.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没人理会小太刀  她总是一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.47,0:03:48.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对孤身一人默默活着的小太刀感兴趣的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.96,0:03:50.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有宅子里的佣人们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.93,0:04:09.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁来…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.54,0:04:12.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.49,0:04:16.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  笕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.87,0:04:19.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你发什么呆呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.17,0:04:23.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方便面要泡烂了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.79,0:04:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.61,0:04:34.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么突然这么叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.45,0:04:38.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想起来以前我是这么叫你的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.81,0:04:41.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前是以前
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.75,0:04:57.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛  居然一脸平静地说出这种话来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.65,0:05:05.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千莉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.98,0:05:07.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚我不会让你睡的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.99,0:05:09.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.16,0:05:15.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  千莉家的通宵放映会  现在开始
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.22,0:05:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这部电影据说很催泪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.26,0:05:26.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出生以来还是第一次这么开心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.00,0:05:31.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不  你可不能这样就满足了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.18,0:05:33.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有水无祭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.69,0:05:36.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来还有一大堆快乐的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.25,0:05:48.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.95,0:05:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久没一起洗澡了  来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.58,0:05:53.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别闹了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.54,0:05:56.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说我们以前也没一起洗过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.95,0:05:58.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.09,0:06:00.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.54,0:06:02.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我先洗了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.08,0:06:16.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.92,0:06:21.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正等我成了牧羊人  你会忘得一干二净
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.23,0:06:26.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我记得就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.75,0:06:30.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  你们要对凪做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.11,0:06:41.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你  你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.66,0:06:42.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.13,0:06:46.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,京太郎哥哥  为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.65,0:06:49.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…我怎么能不管
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.38,0:07:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.59,0:07:22.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你好啊  白崎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.11,0:07:25.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  突然造访
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.13,0:07:36.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个时间来  有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.85,0:07:40.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是很难开口的事情？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.86,0:07:42.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒也…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.60,0:07:44.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.61,0:07:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.51,0:07:48.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.43,0:07:53.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的…男…男…男…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.84,0:07:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.31,0:08:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的咖喱的隐藏调味料是酸奶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.31,0:08:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs18}注：日语中「男朋友」和「咖喱」两词首字音近
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.02,0:08:02.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是么…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.90,0:08:03.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.08,0:08:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次我要说了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.60,0:08:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.54,0:08:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请做我的男朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.74,0:08:27.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.53,0:08:28.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.07,0:08:35.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.38,0:08:38.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.56,0:08:44.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要聊到什么…时候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.89,0:08:52.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位就是姐姐的男朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.78,0:08:54.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.62,0:08:56.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好  我是笕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.06,0:08:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好  我是她妹妹  纱依
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.37,0:09:02.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天真是不好意思  让你特地过来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.49,0:09:05.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐一直跟我讲笕学长你的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.89,0:09:07.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很想见你一面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.46,0:09:10.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才…才没有一直说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.09,0:09:14.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还讲过发传单的京子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.34,0:09:15.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.15,0:09:17.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  笕学长
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.88,0:09:20.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我姐姐做女朋友合格吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.07,0:09:22.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太合格了  配我都浪费了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.05,0:09:25.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笕同学你太会说了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.32,0:09:29.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我姐姐就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.45,0:09:30.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.22,0:09:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然她冒冒失失的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.72,0:09:34.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但她很温柔  还很会做饭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.95,0:09:37.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会成为一个好太太的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.23,0:09:40.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纱依你说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.38,0:09:43.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  那是叫护士的铃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.06,0:09:46.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.84,0:09:50.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是假的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.63,0:09:54.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是姐姐的男朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.30,0:09:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.04,0:10:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐说的汐美学园的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.98,0:10:07.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是为了给我打气而编的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.91,0:10:08.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.86,0:10:12.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并不是责备她
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.97,0:10:16.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我见笕学长你  是想向你道谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.19,0:10:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,道谢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.46,0:10:22.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畏首畏尾的姐姐决定举办水无祭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.35,0:10:26.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想是因为有笕学长你们的支持
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.58,0:10:31.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也是因为白崎而联系在了一起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.43,0:10:34.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很感谢白崎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.77,0:10:36.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.97,0:10:42.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被狠狠地训了一顿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.58,0:10:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  我都听说了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.69,0:10:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.79,0:10:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笕学长说他爱你的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.47,0:10:52.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是恩爱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.92,0:10:58.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱…爱…爱…！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.62,0:10:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白崎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.65,0:11:04.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白崎  你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.54,0:11:10.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后也请多关照姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.26,0:11:18.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天让你陪我做这种事  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.68,0:11:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事  能和纱依妹妹聊天  我很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.41,0:11:25.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笕同学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.89,0:11:30.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为今天的回礼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.89,0:11:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你方便的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.30,0:11:36.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能去你家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.42,0:11:38.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.79,0:11:48.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.60,0:11:52.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了啊  那么慌慌张张的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.07,0:11:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  小太刀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.14,0:12:02.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  你突然是要干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.20,0:12:03.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  暂时先在这呆一会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.34,0:12:11.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.34,0:12:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.09,0:12:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.30,0:12:33.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笕同学居然用着这么可爱的杯子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.89,0:12:38.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得生活需要有些润饰呢就…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.78,0:12:49.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笕同学  味道浓一点比较好吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.72,0:12:52.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.12,0:12:57.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  那件是我中意的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.18,0:13:01.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次给你买新的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.17,0:13:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.92,0:13:06.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像阳台上进来了一只猫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.07,0:13:08.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喵呜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.14,0:13:10.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.00,0:13:12.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.44,0:13:19.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好  我是因正妻归宅而被赶出去的小偷猫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.08,0:13:20.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.03,0:13:21.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笕同学
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.31,0:13:22.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.20,0:13:25.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牧羊人给我发了这样的邮件
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.42,0:13:32.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想用亲手做饭来提高贤妻度吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.57,0:13:33.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是行不通的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.60,0:13:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是自作聪明啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.49,0:13:38.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像跟往常的感觉不太一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.65,0:13:40.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内容也指明了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.35,0:13:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小太刀…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.86,0:13:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想让所有申请的团体都能参加水无祭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.45,0:13:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果因为时间不够而拒绝的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.24,0:13:55.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那跟汐美祭就没什么区别了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.66,0:13:59.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,延长租借日光浴的时间不就好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.74,0:14:01.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样就需要更多的经费
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.03,0:14:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个搞不好  会出现上百万的赤字
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.88,0:14:12.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总而言之  只要聚集来客人就意味着胜利对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.80,0:14:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  乐趣就在于尝试嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.61,0:14:17.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.29,0:14:18.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要说傻话了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.34,0:14:21.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小玉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.77,0:14:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有我在  就绝对不会让赤字发生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.36,0:14:28.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小玉  谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.95,0:14:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纱依  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.96,0:14:41.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以暂时出院了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.29,0:14:44.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.66,0:14:55.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  不会又是白崎吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.32,0:14:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.39,0:14:58.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之先去阳台躲会…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.53,0:15:03.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  要不要来个修罗场啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.99,0:15:06.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在  现在就来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.02,0:15:07.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.01,0:15:10.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小太刀  别冲动
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.54,0:15:13.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白  白崎…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.35,0:15:14.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有何贵干
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.49,0:15:20.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  纱依…我妹妹她无论如何想见笕同学一面…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.70,0:15:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白崎  不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.49,0:15:23.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笕学长
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.35,0:15:27.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨  纱依妹妹  能出院真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.80,0:15:31.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的房间里  为什么会有女人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.74,0:15:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这  这个是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.16,0:15:37.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你解释一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.20,0:15:43.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小太刀学姐  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.08,0:15:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟笕学长是什么关系？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.80,0:15:49.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.43,0:15:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纱依  问这种事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.94,0:15:53.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这跟姐姐你无关
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.60,0:15:55.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是的  咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.27,0:15:58.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小太刀学姐  请告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.80,0:16:01.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的关系吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.45,0:16:03.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  怎么说比较好？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.80,0:16:04.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.61,0:16:10.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小太刀…是我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.72,0:16:16.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹妹！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.33,0:16:27.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笕学长  那是最差劲的借口了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.79,0:16:30.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  都说了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.67,0:16:34.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好过分啊  京太郎  居然说我是你的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.77,0:16:39.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明昨天晚上是那样强烈地贪求我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.56,0:16:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小太刀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.37,0:16:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你别再闹了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.36,0:16:45.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  是妹妹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.19,0:16:49.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  可是  你们两个是同岁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.42,0:16:52.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笕同学你真是伤脑筋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.22,0:16:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白崎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.44,0:16:58.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  这样下去真的好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.89,0:17:00.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纱依？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.09,0:17:02.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.52,0:17:04.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说笕学长是你的男朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.63,0:17:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是骗人的对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.68,0:17:11.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…姐姐你喜欢笕学长  是事实吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.74,0:17:14.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可笕同学他…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.03,0:17:18.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟那无关  重要的是姐姐你的感情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.08,0:17:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纱依  太激动的话会…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.57,0:17:24.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢笕学长的话  就不能放弃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.12,0:17:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能放弃…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.30,0:17:28.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纱依？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.15,0:17:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纱依！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.03,0:17:31.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纱依妹妹！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.12,0:17:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纱依！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.07,0:17:34.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸口很闷吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.51,0:17:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说不能激动啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.85,0:17:39.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  现在就叫救护车来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.69,0:17:41.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来打
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.82,0:17:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纱依  快睁开眼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.37,0:17:46.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纱依  求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.24,0:17:47.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纱依
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.35,0:17:50.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小太刀  我有事求你帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.27,0:17:50.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.27,0:17:54.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用你的力量  带纱依妹妹去医院
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.84,0:17:57.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了  小太刀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.04,0:18:01.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.84,0:18:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纱依…纱依…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.60,0:18:06.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小太刀同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.90,0:18:09.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有办法解决
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.57,0:18:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.92,0:18:22.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能输啊  姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.42,0:18:27.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纱依…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.42,0:18:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笕…同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.72,0:18:43.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.44,0:18:46.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我为什么会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.58,0:18:49.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用在意  已经不要紧了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.15,0:18:58.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纱依她病情好像已经稳定下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.39,0:19:00.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.73,0:19:02.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  笕同学
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.25,0:19:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要道谢的话去向小太刀…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.34,0:19:07.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  好像也没那个必要呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.58,0:19:12.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吓到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.16,0:19:17.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  没想到可以用书来进行移动
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.62,0:19:20.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能通俗易懂地给我解释一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.05,0:19:26.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和小太刀  是类似于牧羊人的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.96,0:19:31.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是说…至今为止的邮件
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.17,0:19:32.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.24,0:19:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有别的牧羊人存在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.06,0:19:40.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还只是个见习的  只能看到模糊的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.99,0:19:44.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到未来…那就是说  那时的事故也是？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.83,0:19:48.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候我跟牧羊人还完全搭不上边
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.53,0:19:56.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早就预料到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.32,0:20:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都是正常来往的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.76,0:20:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦得知了我是个充满谜团的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.08,0:20:10.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不可能再保持原来的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.03,0:20:18.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笕同学
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.75,0:20:23.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…会消失吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.25,0:20:27.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不会消失的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.55,0:20:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是大家会失去与我相关的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.15,0:20:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那跟消失了没什么两样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.78,0:20:40.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要走
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.05,0:20:46.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里都不要去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.88,0:20:48.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白崎…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.05,0:20:57.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望能永远跟你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.52,0:21:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.80,0:21:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白崎…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.51,0:21:22.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个呢  不是希望能够交往什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.13,0:21:24.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是人类间的感情  或者说是生物间的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.61,0:21:28.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.47,0:21:30.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以请不要放在心上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.20,0:21:35.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.89,0:21:38.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.63,0:21:59.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.46,0:22:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笕学长！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.50,0:22:05.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.75,0:22:07.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活动室被…活动室被…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.02,0:22:12.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.21,0:22:15.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.14,0:22:17.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在这干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.28,0:22:19.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么？社团活动啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.96,0:22:22.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们都是图书部员呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.46,0:22:26.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要说傻话了  我可不记得有批准你们入部
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.83,0:22:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为  我们是去年入部的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.55,0:22:31.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.90,0:22:34.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们几个  不是幽灵部员吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.67,0:22:38.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天开始  目标成为模范部员  请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.56,0:22:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请从活动室里出去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.44,0:22:46.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  刚才的部员总会上  我被选为了部长
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.65,0:22:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,委任书在这  看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.40,0:22:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部员的四分之三认可
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.33,0:22:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该出去的是你们
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.19,0:23:05.65,TXTC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\frz351.3\pos(245,249)}『牧羊人不允许你们这样的人存在。』
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.51,0:23:08.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的晚饭吃什么呢~
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.07,0:23:12.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉这样一来  比起妹妹更像新婚妻子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.45,0:23:14.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  这个杯面是新发售的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.40,0:23:16.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个冷冻披萨很好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.33,0:23:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小太刀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.48,0:23:18.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我观察很久了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.44,0:23:20.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果设定是新婚妻子  那种选择不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.63,0:23:22.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了自己  而竭尽全力去做不擅长的菜式  甚至切到手指
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.95,0:23:24.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那副模样可是男人的浪漫所在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.07,0:23:27.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板你和超市一点都不搭调
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.05,0:23:27.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在听我说话吗？
